      "content": "wait so you're saying the wine actually makes it less effective? i thought alcohol helped people fall asleep faster so i figured it would work with the pill. also what's the deal with the magnesium dose? is 500mg a lot to take at once or is that like a normal amount for sleep? i'm really desperate to finally get some rest tonight.",
